        @ByVal
public LongResult Decompress(@Cast(value="int64_t")
                                    long input_len,

                                    long output_buffer_len,

                                    BytePointer output_buffer)
        \brief One-shot decompression function output_buffer_len must be correct and therefore be obtained in advance. The actual decompressed length is returned. \note One-shot decompression is not always compatible with streaming compression. Depending on the codec (e.g. LZ4), different formats may be used.
